  "text": "In [CITATION_1] Huynh-Kha et al. focused on developing a system to detect copy-move and the splicing forgeries together in one image. By applying one-level Discrete Wavelet Transform, the sharped edges with high frequencies were detected from LH, HL and HH sub-bands. The suspicious region was extracted the feature using Run Difference Method (RDM).",
